  "detailed_description": "Automaton Lung is an experimental third-person exploration game.<br><br>Make use of your special abilities to skate, shoot, and fly through over 40 unique locations. In a strange land with almost no information you must be resourceful and clever.<br>Question everything you see and trust nothing you hear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158900/extras/2c9edb690374068db4fbaae5cf2c9b4a.poster.avif?t=1723015274\" width=454 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158900/extras/2c9edb690374068db4fbaae5cf2c9b4a.webm?t=1723015274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158900/extras/2c9edb690374068db4fbaae5cf2c9b4a.mp4?t=1723015274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each footstep taken, every mile flown, and all doorways entered reveal more to discover in Automaton Lung.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158900/extras/7612c7dd59d7e9fac9914c0371d3d216.poster.avif?t=1723015274\" width=454 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158900/extras/7612c7dd59d7e9fac9914c0371d3d216.webm?t=1723015274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158900/extras/7612c7dd59d7e9fac9914c0371d3d216.mp4?t=1723015274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This port adds many helpful configuration settings and graphics options.<br><br>-Play in the original resolution from the Nintendo 3ds release, or in any resolution supported by your monitor.<br>-Steam achievements<br>-Rebind controls however you like<br>-Improved lock-on aiming and other minor control tweaks",
